[Frankly I would be more at ease if the official news release had had details of the vaccination of the livestock in the village of Molokanovsky Ilmensky rural settlement, and of a field investigation team searching for any other animal cases in that village and its neighbouring villages, and to expand the vaccination accordingly. Over the years I have learnt that nature is singularly unconcerned by bureaucratic statements. It is not that she is illiterate but merely reads them for amusement.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map of Russia can be accessed at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2686502,40932. To find Volgograd in southern Russia, go to http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volgograd. To find Krasnooktyabrskiy, go to http://www.gomapper.com/travel/where-is/krasnooktyabrskiy-volgograd-located.html. - Mod.MHJ]
